<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-6971] Clover build doesn&apos;t generate per-test coverage</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-6971</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Because of the way the structure of Hadoop&apos;s builds is done Clover can&apos;t properly detect test classes among the sources. As the result clover reports are incomplete and do not provide viral per-test coverage info.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
